high_descs: Take a step forward then take step to your right and then walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the right side of the green table to your left and turn left when you get to the right side of it.
Pick up the bowl that's in front of you.
Turn left and walk to the fridge that's in front of you so you're facing the fridge
Chill the bowl in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the left of center of the green table on your right and when you get just to the left of center turn right and walk to it.
Put the bowl near the green table's left corner near you.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and then left again before turning left to face the bowl on the green table.
Pick the bowl up from the green table.
Go left and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick the bowl up again.
Go right and then turn to the right to face the green table.
Put the bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on a table.

high_descs: Walk around to face the other side of the table.
Pick up the gray bowl from the table.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the bowl inside of the fridge, close the door, open the door, take the bowl out of the fridge, and close the drawer.
Turn right to face the kitchen island.
Put the bowl down on the left side of the island.
anns.task_desc: To chill a bowl and put it on the kitchen island.
